      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STORMY DAY (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 2.5 lengths at Murray Bridge in a handy 22.04 beating Lone Rooster. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to his credit. Looks the testing material. MAZUMA MAYHEM (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (17.03) in a Other at this track. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and eight minor placings to his name from 18 starts. Can measure up this time. YVONNE'S PICK (5) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 3rd at this track over 300m. Expected to feature again. FORGOTTEN FURY (1) is worth a look over a shorter journey this time.",
